# Use from Pine to pipe an uncaught spam to SpamAssassin's learn tool.

#--------------------------------------------------------------------------
# $RCSfile$
#--------------------------------------------------------------------------
# $Revision: 2 $
# $Date: 2004-02-25 12:53:24 -0500 (Wed, 25 Feb 2004) $
# $Author: dmorelli $
#
# Script to teach SpamAssassin that an email is not spam.
#--------------------------------------------------------------------------

sa-learn --spam --no-rebuild $1

